{"tid":180464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手　被炒　易患適應性障礙","createTime":"2017-03-31T02:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T03:16:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa9844fc8e1ec095540b31c357c441bf89b8140","tid":180464,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19975254&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19975254%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170331&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=be3d8c1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19975254%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170331&h=d95a9f10\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19975254&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170331</a><br />\n<br />\n分手　被炒　易患適應性障礙<br />\n<br />\n健康與醫療&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n沙田醫院精神科副顧問醫生林煒指持續失眠、脾氣突然變得暴躁，都是情緒病先兆。周智堅攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】情緒健康不容忽視，沙田醫院精神科副顧問醫生林煒表示，精神科門診個案有上升趨勢，以威爾斯親王醫院為例，精神科門診現時每年有5萬至5.2萬求診人次，持續失眠、脾氣突然變得暴躁，都是情緒病先兆，呼籲港人正視。<br />\n<br />\n脾氣突暴躁為警號<br />\n<br />\n林指，增加的求診個案中，多數因工作、家庭問題包括婚姻、管教子女，帶來種種壓力及情緒問題。當中不乏從事金融、教學工作的人。除了工作量大引起壓力，人事問題都很重要，包括與同事或上司「夾唔嚟」。<br />\n常見求診的情緒病包括「適應性障礙」（Adjustment Disorder），例如與伴侶分手或被解僱，引致情緒困擾，其次包括抑鬱症、焦慮症等。林稱，「經常瞓唔到」要留意。失眠可以由不同的情緒病引起，建議盡快求診。另外，脾氣突然變得暴躁也是另一情緒病警號，不能掉以輕心。<br />\n■記者梁麗兒<br />\n<br />\n想輕輕鬆鬆健康啲，記住留意健康蘋台<br />\n<a href=\"http://health.appledaily.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhealth.appledaily.com.hk%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4f25afd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://health.appledaily.com.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"4fba647e7b835fae5f6edcb9866ee2097775019e","tid":180464,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"適應 性障礙"}]}